<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>4</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《道藏要籍选刊</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&middot;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西升经》第</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">642页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
